li.al:
the term “road vehicle” shall mean not only any
						  powerdriven road vehicle but also any trailer or semi-trailer designed to be
						  coupled thereto;

the term “heavy or bulky goods” shall mean any heavy or
						  bulky object which because of its weight, size or nature is not normally
						  carried in a closed road vehicle or closed container;

no goods can be removed from, or introduced into, the sealed
					 part of the vehicle without leaving obvious traces of tampering or without
					 breaking the Customs seal;

