following fastenings shall be
used;

li.al:
steel
wire ropes of at least 3 mm diameter;
or

ropes of hemp or sisal of at least
8 mm diameter encased in a transparent sheath of unstretchable plastic;
or

permit
				the competent authority to examine further units at any time during the
				production of the type series concerned;

mark the road vehicles in a visible place with the
				identification numbers or letters of the design-type and the serial number of
				the vehicle in the type series (manufacturer's number);

no goods can be removed from, or introduced
				into, the sealed part of the container without leaving visible traces of
